title: Wholesale Prices of Metal and Metal Products for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1890-1951 (2)--Original Data, 1947-1956. 73 Items Are Included In The Index For 1890-1925 And 129 Items For 1926-1951. Source: Bls Bulletins And "Wholesale Prices" Through 1941; Thereafter Bulletin Nos. 736, 759, 785, 870, 877, 920, 947, 973, 1007, And 1083 Through 1950; Monthly Labor Review, 1952 Issues, For 1951.

This NBER data series m04066a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
